  <brief_title>Analysis of Respiratory Variations of the Right Internal Jugular Vein as a Predictor of Fluid Responsiveness During Mechanical Ventilation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Analysis of Respiratory Variations of the Internal Jugular Vein as a Predictor of Fluid Responsiveness During Mechanical Ventilation</official_title>
